  }, "v11"), mdx("p", null, "\xD4ng li\u1EC1n sai m\u1ED9t \u0111\u1EA7y t\u1EDB kh\xE1c. Ch\xFAng c\u0169ng \u0111\xE1nh \u0111\u1EADp lu\xF4n, ch\u1EB3ng n\u1EC3 \xF4ng ch\xFAt n\xE0o, r\u1ED3i c\u0169ng \u0111u\u1ED5i v\u1EC1 tay kh\xF4ng. "), mdx("h6", {
