  }, "v19"), mdx("p", null, "C\xE1c gi\xE1o s\u01B0 lu\u1EADt v\xE0 c\xE1c gi\u1EDBi tr\u01B0\u1EDFng t\u1EBF mu\u1ED1n b\u1EAFt Ch\xFAa Gi\xEA-xu ngay l\u1EADp t\u1EE9c v\xEC h\u1ECD bi\u1EBFt c\xE2u chuy\u1EC7n \u1EA5y \xE1m ch\u1EC9 h\u1ECD, nh\u01B0ng h\u1ECD s\u1EE3 d\xE2n ch\xFAng ph\u1EA3n \u1EE9ng.C\xF3 n\xEAn \u0111\xF3ng thu\u1EBF hay kh\xF4ng? "), mdx("h6", {
    "id": "v20"
