  }, "v29"), mdx("p", null, "Trong chuy\u1EC7n n\u1EA7y c\xF3 t\u1EA5t c\u1EA3 b\u1EA3y anh em trai. Ng\u01B0\u1EDDi anh c\u1EA3 l\u1EA5y v\u1EE3, r\u1ED3i ch\u1EBFt kh\xF4ng con. "), mdx("h6", {
